,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"我相信和理非係有佢嘅威力，起碼可以召集多好多人（所以唔好再話有人企喺橋上面唔去打，上面99%都係和理非，肯出嚟已經好好，好過唔出嚟喺屋企睇電視嘅多多聲）<br />\n<br />\n人多有咩分別？<br />\n如果冇「人多勢眾」作backup，示威者就會好容易好似9號夜晚比警察前後包抄<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家唔好自己人互鬧，變相陷入三毛最想見到嘅分化局面"},{"pid":"2aca88c83d26cc26ada0cb72e23ef2604b4af05a","tid":1216121,"uid":10653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:29:47.000Z","msg":"正路今次訴求要加埋<br />\n1. 立即釋放被捕示威者<br />\n2. 提供免費醫療服務比因為示威入院嘅傷者"},{"pid":"206f58c32f7b63f9cf5d5bd5da84ba2422e691b9","tid":1216121,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3753811687622ece99dd46b9ca0ecbba1ba9774","tid":1216121,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"星期日既遊行，大家一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你會諗，上星期行完政府咪又係唔理，有鬼用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係，連續兩星期整個城市有1/7以上既人出黎抗議係從未見過<br />\n就算只係和理非，港共政權亦無面對過咁強大而持續既民意 (0371 只係one-off 50萬人上街)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用打拳黎做比喻，上星期既遊行佢硬食已經少咁一半血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n612既暴力鎮壓之後港共政權既合法性已經殘血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家全世界，無論係美國、英國、歐盟、台灣、NGO、人權組織、評級機構都搵緊機會補刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果星期日再有過百萬人上街，就等如港共諗住就黎捱到計技術分果陣中咗一下sucker punch！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係最大機會令佢陷入完全管治危機，向民意跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論你以往覺得遊行幾廢幾冇用都好，今次都一定要去，多你一個絕對好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期日見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77773e8981652d3bd70c046e29e0ba16873506f","tid":1216121,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e239ab3a4e6c89a6373b87d075108a556ad9face","tid":1216121,"uid":133608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"好似記者咁戴住頭盔防毒面罩去！"},{"pid":"7a3c37dc09071043807e34c743dd0ae5d8caad8a","tid":1216121,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c7a4399d143c0950b3bfbb45816266976dcfbc","tid":1216121,"uid":17055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980ebc66f11e8d6322329feb654b28167415f064","tid":1216121,"uid":254594,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"好大機會少過上次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:44:26.000Z","msg":"Sad but true, 一陣人數小左又比位林奠入"},{"pid":"504562bfa6f3ee9398d31b3d85ef0870c1105f35","tid":1216121,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ef2d0f42dca76a8a01856aa9a4cb334ec51240","tid":1216121,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:01:57.000Z","msg":"終點禮賓府ok?"}]}